(183, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/04/improvements-to-wordpress-org/''>Improvements to WordPress.org</a> <span class="rss-date">4 kwietnia 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">If you visit WordPress.org regularly you might have noticed some changes around the place. If you don’t, now’s the time to check them out! We’ve been working hard to improve the site to make it more useful to everyone, both developers and users, and we hope you like what we’ve done. New Theme and Plugin Directories [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/group-and-filter-plugins-by-functionality-with-plugin-groups-by-calderawp''>WPTavern: Group and Filter Plugins by Functionality with Plugin Groups by CalderaWP</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/ithemes-patches-vulnerability-that-affects-all-versions-of-the-ithemes-security-plugin''>WPTavern: iThemes Patches Vulnerability that Affects All Versions of the iThemes Security Plugin</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wordpress-for-android-version-3-9-adds-two-factor-authentication-and-improvements-to-the-media-library''>WPTavern: WordPress for Android Version 3.9 Adds Two-Factor Authentication and Improvements to the Media Library</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popularna wtyczka:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/all-in-one-wp-security-and-firewall/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>All In One WP Security &amp; Firewall</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=all-in-one-wp-security-and-firewall&amp;_wpnonce=00a3922948&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''All In One WP Security &amp; Firewall''>Zainstaluj</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
